visual.name: CalendarVisualByMAQSoftware
visual.description: View key events directly on your Power BI reports with a calendar view.

pt-PT.visual_enableright: Ativar o layout da direita para a esquerda

dataRoles.description: Add URL column. Enable navigation on event's double click
dataRoles.name: EventURL

startingWeekDay.description: Select week name to set start day of the week

currentTimeLine.description: Show current time line for 'day' and 'week' view

navLink.description: Click on 'dates' or 'week Number' to navigate to day or week

rtl.description: Display calendar orientation from right to left

captionValue.description: Caption value stores the persisted data color values

cellCaptionValue.description: Caption value stores the persited data color values for cells
